[http://www.iso.org/iso/en/CatalogueDetailPage.CatalogueDetail?CSNUMBER=30123 "ISO 7027: Water quality -- Determination of turbidity."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iso.org/iso/en/CatalogueDetailPage.CatalogueDetail?CSNUMBER=30123 |date=20050109064334 }} 1999.</ref>
